+- `runtime/logs/codex-patlas-exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit-step-002-receptionist-search-attempt-003.md`
+
+## Output
+
+- `REPORT.md` with one interaction-template sheet and one downstream-gate
+  ledger for the promoted candidates.
+- `REPORT-SUMMARY.md` with the Step-3 readiness verdict.
