+### 2. Windowed Spectator-Leakage Budget
+
+- `[PROPOSED]` Exact criterion:
+
+  ```text
+  Let
+
+    D_on(t)
+      := |Q_clk(t)| + |Q_seed(t)| + |Q_amp(t)|
+         + |Q_rot^A(t)| + |Q_rot^D(t)| + |Q_next(t)|.
