+- `runtime/logs/codex-patlas-exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit-step-002-receptionist-search-attempt-003.md`
+
+## Output
+
+- `REPORT.md` with the candidate menu, exact criteria, and promotion / rejection
+  decisions.
+- `REPORT-SUMMARY.md` with the bounded shortlist and the main definition-level
+  lesson.
