+    Delta_tmpl(P_n; I)
+      := sup_{t in I}
+         || Pi_{P_n} N(u,u)(t) - F_h(U_{P_n}(t)) ||_role
+         /
+         ( || F_h(U_{P_n}(t)) ||_role + eps_ref ),
+
+    Delta_spec(P_n; I)
+      := sup_{t in I}
+         || Pi_{S_n} N(u,u)(t) ||_role
+         /
+         ( || F_h(U_{P_n}(t)) ||_role + eps_ref ).
+
+  Candidate condition:
+
+    Delta_tmpl <= lambda_tmpl
+    and
